1
00:00:19,998 --> 00:00:21,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han.</font>

2
00:00:40,098 --> 00:00:41,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Find her.</font>

3
00:00:54,098 --> 00:00:56,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Did they hurt you?</font>

4
00:00:56,598 --> 00:00:58,228
<font color=#FFFF00>You've been well, right?</font>

5
00:01:15,098 --> 00:01:16,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

6
00:01:17,468 --> 00:01:18,998
<font color=#FFFF00>I found out too late.</font>

7
00:01:20,198 --> 00:01:22,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I should have looked for you before.</font>

8
00:01:25,068 --> 00:01:26,098
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

9
00:01:28,568 --> 00:01:30,898
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what's happening.</font>

10
00:01:32,528 --> 00:01:33,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm...</font>

11
00:01:34,868 --> 00:01:36,168
<font color=#FFFF00>so confused.</font>

12
00:01:47,368 --> 00:01:48,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

13
00:01:49,068 --> 00:01:50,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen to me carefully.</font>

14
00:01:51,868 --> 00:01:54,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry. Just wait for me.</font>

15
00:01:55,228 --> 00:01:57,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Do what Chairman Bang wants you to do.</font>

16
00:01:57,268 --> 00:01:58,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't go against them.</font>

17
00:01:59,568 --> 00:02:02,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Trust me and wait for me.</font>

18
00:02:03,128 --> 00:02:04,128
<font color=#FFFF00>You can do that for me, right?</font>

19
00:02:04,798 --> 00:02:06,068
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you going to do?</font>

20
00:02:06,728 --> 00:02:09,468
<font color=#FFFF00>What if that puts you in danger too?</font>

21
00:02:10,468 --> 00:02:11,698
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think that will happen.</font>

22
00:02:12,868 --> 00:02:14,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I will resolve this problem by all means.</font>

23
00:02:14,668 --> 00:02:16,068
<font color=#FFFF00>I will make sure to...</font>

24
00:02:16,568 --> 00:02:18,298
<font color=#FFFF00>get you and your grandmother out of that house.</font>

25
00:02:29,798 --> 00:02:31,068
<font color=#FFFF00>I missed you.</font>

26
00:02:33,498 --> 00:02:34,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I missed you too.</font>

27
00:02:45,828 --> 00:02:47,698
<font color=#FFFF00>(Episode 45)</font>

28
00:02:53,428 --> 00:02:55,628
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened? What's the matter?</font>

29
00:02:55,898 --> 00:02:58,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui disappeared.</font>

30
00:02:58,968 --> 00:03:00,028
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

31
00:03:02,228 --> 00:03:03,968
<font color=#FFFF00>What were you doing?</font>

32
00:03:04,068 --> 00:03:06,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you kidding me? Go find her.</font>

33
00:03:06,968 --> 00:03:07,998
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.</font>

34
00:03:08,428 --> 00:03:09,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

35
00:03:14,368 --> 00:03:15,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

36
00:03:16,068 --> 00:03:17,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you receive the script I sent you?</font>

37
00:03:18,628 --> 00:03:19,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

38
00:03:20,928 --> 00:03:21,998
<font color=#FFFF00>You did a very good job.</font>

39
00:03:23,698 --> 00:03:25,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Once you get home,</font>

40
00:03:25,328 --> 00:03:27,898
<font color=#FFFF00>don't worry about anything and just work on your script.</font>

41
00:03:28,068 --> 00:03:29,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay?</font>

42
00:03:30,598 --> 00:03:32,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. But...</font>

43
00:03:32,698 --> 00:03:33,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Just listen to me.</font>

44
00:03:34,298 --> 00:03:36,328
<font color=#FFFF00>And take good care of Ms. Oh.</font>

45
00:04:00,268 --> 00:04:01,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

46
00:04:03,228 --> 00:04:04,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I love you.</font>

47
00:04:08,128 --> 00:04:09,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I love you too.</font>

48
00:04:21,068 --> 00:04:22,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

49
00:04:27,498 --> 00:04:29,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I think she left the building.</font>

50
00:04:29,768 --> 00:04:32,568
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - I can't find her anywhere.</font>

51
00:04:33,428 --> 00:04:34,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

52
00:04:39,768 --> 00:04:41,128
<font color=#FFFF00>There she is.</font>

53
00:04:46,468 --> 00:04:47,498
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

54
00:04:50,728 --> 00:04:53,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Where have you been?</font>

55
00:04:54,598 --> 00:04:56,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I went to the bathroom. Why?</font>

56
00:05:02,228 --> 00:05:04,728
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have told me before going to the bathroom.</font>

57
00:05:08,398 --> 00:05:10,328
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let's go. - Yes, sir.</font>

58
00:05:47,328 --> 00:05:49,368
<font color=#FFFF00>- Who are you? - Well...</font>

59
00:05:50,298 --> 00:05:52,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm from FGC.</font>

60
00:05:52,468 --> 00:05:54,598
<font color=#FFFF00>- Can I talk to her for a minute? - Okay.</font>

61
00:06:08,028 --> 00:06:09,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Chairwoman Park Chang Wook.</font>

62
00:06:15,498 --> 00:06:16,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello.</font>

63
00:06:16,968 --> 00:06:19,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm Han Seong Joon. Ms. Oh Gui Boon asked me to come and see you.</font>

64
00:06:23,998 --> 00:06:26,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm here to help you.</font>

65
00:06:44,868 --> 00:06:45,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

66
00:07:37,228 --> 00:07:38,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Choi Jin Sung is...</font>

67
00:07:38,598 --> 00:07:40,268
<font color=#FFFF00>all that remains.</font>

68
00:07:40,998 --> 00:07:42,898
<font color=#FFFF00>He is the key figure.</font>

69
00:07:43,798 --> 00:07:45,328
<font color=#FFFF00>If Director Choi helps us,</font>

70
00:07:45,598 --> 00:07:47,428
<font color=#FFFF00>things would be a lot easier.</font>

71
00:07:48,568 --> 00:07:50,898
<font color=#FFFF00>What did the chairwoman say?</font>

72
00:07:51,628 --> 00:07:54,328
<font color=#FFFF00>If all the people on the list resigned from the company,</font>

73
00:07:55,228 --> 00:07:57,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I should get the key from Ms. Oh, unlock the safe...</font>

74
00:07:58,428 --> 00:08:00,768
<font color=#FFFF00>and hand everything in it to Bang Gwang Jin, she said.</font>

75
00:08:03,898 --> 00:08:05,368
<font color=#FFFF00>She's trying to raise the stakes.</font>

76
00:08:06,368 --> 00:08:07,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Then...</font>

77
00:08:07,768 --> 00:08:10,668
<font color=#FFFF00>on the day Bang Gwang Jin announces the renewed will,</font>

78
00:08:11,168 --> 00:08:14,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Chairwoman Park will return to the company.</font>

79
00:08:21,398 --> 00:08:22,428
<font color=#FFFF00>This is...</font>

80
00:08:23,128 --> 00:08:24,528
<font color=#FFFF00>the key to the safe.</font>

81
00:08:25,968 --> 00:08:27,228
<font color=#FFFF00>She set you...</font>

82
00:08:27,968 --> 00:08:29,668
<font color=#FFFF00>such a heavy burden.</font>

83
00:08:37,928 --> 00:08:39,568
<font color=#FFFF00>There are Chairwoman Park's will...</font>

84
00:08:39,868 --> 00:08:42,298
<font color=#FFFF00>and the truth about Bang Hyun Jeong who is supposedly dead.</font>

85
00:08:43,568 --> 00:08:44,828
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a secret...</font>

86
00:08:45,528 --> 00:08:48,068
<font color=#FFFF00>that they've tried to keep for their entire lives.</font>

87
00:08:49,728 --> 00:08:50,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Please...</font>

88
00:08:51,498 --> 00:08:52,998
<font color=#FFFF00>take good care of it.</font>

89
00:09:00,728 --> 00:09:01,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

90
00:09:03,528 --> 00:09:06,268
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you keep your old mother...</font>

91
00:09:06,268 --> 00:09:07,728
<font color=#FFFF00>locked up like that?</font>

92
00:09:08,138 --> 00:09:09,868
<font color=#FFFF00>That's so inhumane.</font>

93
00:09:10,098 --> 00:09:11,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Get off me.</font>

94
00:09:11,198 --> 00:09:12,998
<font color=#FFFF00>All the women in our family...</font>

95
00:09:12,998 --> 00:09:15,028
<font color=#FFFF00>are so talkative.</font>

96
00:09:16,068 --> 00:09:17,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Where have you been?</font>

97
00:09:19,468 --> 00:09:20,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you...</font>

98
00:09:20,798 --> 00:09:22,068
<font color=#FFFF00>I went to see your grandmother.</font>

99
00:09:22,498 --> 00:09:23,638
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

100
00:09:25,568 --> 00:09:26,898
<font color=#FFFF00>You knew it, right?</font>

101
00:09:28,228 --> 00:09:29,928
<font color=#FFFF00>You knew the whole thing.</font>

102
00:09:32,028 --> 00:09:33,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe this.</font>

103
00:09:34,098 --> 00:09:37,138
<font color=#FFFF00>You guys are so terrible.</font>

104
00:09:37,898 --> 00:09:40,898
<font color=#FFFF00>How could a son and a granddaughter...</font>

105
00:09:41,568 --> 00:09:43,828
<font color=#FFFF00>lock their mother and grandmother...</font>

106
00:09:43,828 --> 00:09:45,968
<font color=#FFFF00>in a mountain for 20 years?</font>

107
00:09:46,498 --> 00:09:49,398
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth do you gain from this?</font>

108
00:09:50,068 --> 00:09:51,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Shut your mouth.</font>

109
00:09:51,498 --> 00:09:53,368
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you say such a thing to us?</font>

110
00:09:53,368 --> 00:09:56,068
<font color=#FFFF00>You should shut your mouth. You know I'm older than you!</font>

111
00:09:56,228 --> 00:09:59,598
<font color=#FFFF00>It's so noisy. Just stop the quarrel.</font>

112
00:10:01,068 --> 00:10:03,598
<font color=#FFFF00>So are you the one...</font>

113
00:10:04,068 --> 00:10:05,928
<font color=#FFFF00>who killed my dad...</font>

114
00:10:06,468 --> 00:10:07,698
<font color=#FFFF00>and mom?</font>

115
00:10:07,828 --> 00:10:10,198
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not it. I told you I didn't do that.</font>

116
00:10:11,138 --> 00:10:12,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm under a false accusation.</font>

117
00:10:12,668 --> 00:10:13,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe this.</font>

118
00:10:14,898 --> 00:10:16,298
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't do this.</font>

119
00:10:16,868 --> 00:10:18,868
<font color=#FFFF00>It just doesn't make sense.</font>

120
00:10:20,668 --> 00:10:22,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Excuse me, Chairman Bang.</font>

121
00:10:22,428 --> 00:10:23,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Mi Joo.</font>

122
00:10:24,728 --> 00:10:26,368
<font color=#FFFF00>As I said before,</font>

123
00:10:26,768 --> 00:10:28,638
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not interested...</font>

124
00:10:28,638 --> 00:10:30,528
<font color=#FFFF00>in the money, power, and reputation.</font>

125
00:10:30,668 --> 00:10:32,098
<font color=#FFFF00>They are no better than trash to me.</font>

126
00:10:32,638 --> 00:10:35,268
<font color=#FFFF00>So let me and my grandmother...</font>

127
00:10:35,668 --> 00:10:37,398
<font color=#FFFF00>get out of here immediately.</font>

128
00:10:37,868 --> 00:10:39,228
<font color=#FFFF00>What have we done wrong?</font>

129
00:10:40,068 --> 00:10:42,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I've known nothing all my life.</font>

130
00:10:43,168 --> 00:10:46,568
<font color=#FFFF00>And my grandmother has lived in adversity until now...</font>

131
00:10:46,698 --> 00:10:47,898
<font color=#FFFF00>just for Chairwoman Park.</font>

132
00:10:50,068 --> 00:10:52,728
<font color=#FFFF00>We will live in obscurity...</font>

133
00:10:53,098 --> 00:10:54,698
<font color=#FFFF00>as we have done so far.</font>

134
00:10:55,428 --> 00:10:56,968
<font color=#FFFF00>So please let us out.</font>

135
00:11:01,598 --> 00:11:02,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry about it.</font>

136
00:11:03,228 --> 00:11:06,298
<font color=#FFFF00>I was going to let you out anyway.</font>

137
00:11:06,628 --> 00:11:08,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Chairwoman Park will rewrite...</font>

138
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,768
<font color=#FFFF00>her will pretty soon.</font>

139
00:11:10,768 --> 00:11:12,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Just wait quietly until then.</font>

140
00:11:12,868 --> 00:11:15,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to keep you here anymore.</font>

141
00:11:16,198 --> 00:11:17,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Send her up to her room.</font>

142
00:11:18,998 --> 00:11:20,398
<font color=#FFFF00>You jerks.</font>

143
00:11:20,528 --> 00:11:22,368
<font color=#FFFF00>All of you will pay for this.</font>

144
00:11:22,498 --> 00:11:24,028
<font color=#FFFF00>You will be punished for this.</font>

145
00:11:24,298 --> 00:11:27,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Bang Mi Joo, I'm not going to be sitting still.</font>

146
00:11:27,568 --> 00:11:29,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Get off me!</font>

147
00:11:29,828 --> 00:11:31,668
<font color=#FFFF00>- Gosh. - Dad.</font>

148
00:11:31,698 --> 00:11:34,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you take Dong Hui there?</font>

149
00:11:34,498 --> 00:11:37,798
<font color=#FFFF00>It is the easiest way to change your grandmother's mind.</font>

150
00:11:38,028 --> 00:11:39,028
<font color=#FFFF00>So what?</font>

151
00:11:39,268 --> 00:11:41,098
<font color=#FFFF00>If she rewrites her will,</font>

152
00:11:41,628 --> 00:11:44,268
<font color=#FFFF00>what will happen to Dong Hui?</font>

153
00:11:44,398 --> 00:11:45,598
<font color=#FFFF00>It's simple.</font>

154
00:11:46,028 --> 00:11:47,498
<font color=#FFFF00>She just said that.</font>

155
00:11:47,828 --> 00:11:49,198
<font color=#FFFF00>She'll live as Oh Dong Hui.</font>

156
00:11:49,228 --> 00:11:50,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it even possible?</font>

157
00:11:51,698 --> 00:11:53,728
<font color=#FFFF00>You know she's Bang Hyun Jeong.</font>

158
00:11:54,628 --> 00:11:56,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Dong Hui is Bang Hyun Jeong. So what?</font>

159
00:11:57,328 --> 00:11:59,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll be getting all the money and stocks...</font>

160
00:11:59,828 --> 00:12:01,868
<font color=#FFFF00>for Bang Hyun Jeong.</font>

161
00:12:02,768 --> 00:12:05,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Jeong will be just an empty shell.</font>

162
00:12:05,068 --> 00:12:06,528
<font color=#FFFF00>She'll be useless.</font>

163
00:12:07,028 --> 00:12:09,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad, please.</font>

164
00:12:11,968 --> 00:12:13,798
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to see them anymore.</font>

165
00:12:14,798 --> 00:12:17,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Just wait a little longer.</font>

166
00:12:18,128 --> 00:12:19,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Everything will be over soon.</font>

167
00:12:26,828 --> 00:12:27,968
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

168
00:12:31,828 --> 00:12:33,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Make some noise when you get in the house.</font>

169
00:12:33,428 --> 00:12:35,268
<font color=#FFFF00>You said you weren't interested.</font>

170
00:12:35,798 --> 00:12:38,168
<font color=#FFFF00>You were doing some research about UN Production.</font>

171
00:12:40,098 --> 00:12:41,398
<font color=#FFFF00>That's just my job...</font>

172
00:12:41,498 --> 00:12:42,668
<font color=#FFFF00>to analyze companies.</font>

173
00:12:42,798 --> 00:12:44,168
<font color=#FFFF00>As a matter of fact,</font>

174
00:12:44,398 --> 00:12:46,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I've done some research on UN Production.</font>

175
00:12:46,968 --> 00:12:49,368
<font color=#FFFF00>As you know, it is a nasty company.</font>

176
00:12:50,098 --> 00:12:53,698
<font color=#FFFF00>I believe you should let Sang Woo wash his hands of the matter.</font>

177
00:12:53,868 --> 00:12:55,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I said I was just looking.</font>

178
00:12:56,428 --> 00:12:58,728
<font color=#FFFF00>You should sell all the stocks of FGC Group.</font>

179
00:12:59,198 --> 00:13:00,968
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no reason to keep them.</font>

180
00:13:01,428 --> 00:13:04,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I think it's better to keep them for a little longer.</font>

181
00:13:05,728 --> 00:13:06,968
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

182
00:13:07,428 --> 00:13:09,498
<font color=#FFFF00>According to our agent,</font>

183
00:13:09,928 --> 00:13:12,598
<font color=#FFFF00>there's a rumor that Park Chang Wook is coming back.</font>

184
00:13:14,668 --> 00:13:16,398
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

185
00:13:16,798 --> 00:13:18,898
<font color=#FFFF00>How can the former chairwoman of FGC group come back?</font>

186
00:13:18,898 --> 00:13:21,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Recently, a rumor has been going around among shareholders...</font>

187
00:13:21,968 --> 00:13:24,998
<font color=#FFFF00>that Chairwoman Park has been found.</font>

188
00:13:27,328 --> 00:13:29,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Whoever it is, he's recklessly bold.</font>

189
00:13:30,128 --> 00:13:31,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Pardon?</font>

190
00:13:31,128 --> 00:13:32,868
<font color=#FFFF00>The return of the chairwoman...</font>

191
00:13:32,868 --> 00:13:34,998
<font color=#FFFF00>must be a very bad news for Bang Gwang Jin.</font>

192
00:13:36,698 --> 00:13:38,668
<font color=#FFFF00>The fact that this rumor is spreading means that...</font>

193
00:13:38,668 --> 00:13:42,128
<font color=#FFFF00>someone's planning to take down Bang Gwang Jin.</font>

194
00:13:42,628 --> 00:13:44,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, I guess that's possible.</font>

195
00:13:45,528 --> 00:13:47,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Should I look into it and find out who's behind it?</font>

196
00:13:47,728 --> 00:13:49,368
<font color=#FFFF00>No, there's no need.</font>

197
00:13:50,098 --> 00:13:53,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Whether it's good news or bad news, it doesn't affect us at all.</font>

198
00:13:54,028 --> 00:13:56,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Like what you said, we should just sell the stocks...</font>

199
00:13:56,868 --> 00:13:59,198
<font color=#FFFF00>at the right time and go back.</font>

200
00:13:59,468 --> 00:14:01,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I will report to you...</font>

201
00:14:01,568 --> 00:14:02,728
<font color=#FFFF00>as soon as I get an update.</font>

202
00:14:03,898 --> 00:14:06,468
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, what will you do about Sang Woo?</font>

203
00:14:07,228 --> 00:14:08,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I said I'm not interested.</font>

204
00:14:09,528 --> 00:14:10,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Still,</font>

205
00:14:10,868 --> 00:14:13,298
<font color=#FFFF00>you have to get him out of UN Production immediately.</font>

206
00:14:15,928 --> 00:14:17,128
<font color=#FFFF00>He's an idiot.</font>

207
00:14:21,128 --> 00:14:22,168
<font color=#FFFF00>It's...</font>

208
00:14:23,228 --> 00:14:25,098
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the old lady who used to live across the street.</font>

209
00:14:34,298 --> 00:14:36,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Your house is bigger than it looks.</font>

210
00:14:37,828 --> 00:14:39,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello.</font>

211
00:14:42,428 --> 00:14:43,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Can I take a seat?</font>

212
00:14:43,928 --> 00:14:45,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure. Take a seat, please.</font>

213
00:14:48,968 --> 00:14:49,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you want some tea?</font>

214
00:14:49,998 --> 00:14:51,428
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't need anything.</font>

215
00:14:51,868 --> 00:14:53,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Why don't you sit?</font>

216
00:14:58,798 --> 00:15:00,898
<font color=#FFFF00>You should sit too, Mr. Gray Hair.</font>

217
00:15:01,468 --> 00:15:02,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure.</font>

218
00:15:09,798 --> 00:15:10,928
<font color=#FFFF00>These are...</font>

219
00:15:12,368 --> 00:15:15,228
<font color=#FFFF00>gochujang and doenjang from our rooftop.</font>

220
00:15:15,628 --> 00:15:17,728
<font color=#FFFF00>These days, men live well...</font>

221
00:15:17,728 --> 00:15:19,628
<font color=#FFFF00>even when they live alone.</font>

222
00:15:20,828 --> 00:15:23,228
<font color=#FFFF00>You shouldn't eat just anything because you're alone.</font>

223
00:15:23,598 --> 00:15:26,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Store-bought ones are not good.</font>

224
00:15:26,568 --> 00:15:28,098
<font color=#FFFF00>You should taste ours.</font>

225
00:15:32,768 --> 00:15:34,468
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't have to do this.</font>

226
00:15:34,468 --> 00:15:36,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I want to give it to you?</font>

227
00:15:36,298 --> 00:15:39,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm giving it to you because you took care of Ah In the other day!</font>

228
00:15:39,028 --> 00:15:40,798
<font color=#FFFF00>You are an incarnation of vengeance.</font>

229
00:15:40,798 --> 00:15:42,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma'am.</font>

230
00:15:42,098 --> 00:15:43,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me finish.</font>

231
00:15:45,668 --> 00:15:47,268
<font color=#FFFF00>When you become as old as me,</font>

232
00:15:48,568 --> 00:15:51,968
<font color=#FFFF00>you learn to separate one thing from another.</font>

233
00:15:52,368 --> 00:15:54,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if I am really mad at you and I want to kill you,</font>

234
00:15:55,168 --> 00:15:57,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I still have to thank you for what you've done for Ah In.</font>

235
00:15:57,668 --> 00:15:59,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if I'm really thankful to you,</font>

236
00:15:59,768 --> 00:16:02,328
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to confront you about what you did to us.</font>

237
00:16:03,668 --> 00:16:04,768
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not...</font>

238
00:16:05,128 --> 00:16:06,698
<font color=#FFFF00>that I don't understand...</font>

239
00:16:07,198 --> 00:16:09,598
<font color=#FFFF00>where you're coming from.</font>

240
00:16:10,128 --> 00:16:11,328
<font color=#FFFF00>To experience such tragedy...</font>

241
00:16:11,768 --> 00:16:15,098
<font color=#FFFF00>must've been so horrifying.</font>

242
00:16:15,928 --> 00:16:18,868
<font color=#FFFF00>You were the eldest son to your father,</font>

243
00:16:20,068 --> 00:16:21,728
<font color=#FFFF00>and you were the elder brother...</font>

244
00:16:22,198 --> 00:16:23,468
<font color=#FFFF00>to your little brother.</font>

245
00:16:24,998 --> 00:16:25,998
<font color=#FFFF00>But still,</font>

246
00:16:26,568 --> 00:16:29,628
<font color=#FFFF00>you were just a sixth grader.</font>

247
00:16:30,068 --> 00:16:32,628
<font color=#FFFF00>When you were supposed to be cared by your parents,</font>

248
00:16:33,298 --> 00:16:34,828
<font color=#FFFF00>your father died,</font>

249
00:16:35,398 --> 00:16:37,268
<font color=#FFFF00>and you lost your little brother.</font>

250
00:16:37,898 --> 00:16:40,228
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ma'am. - Be quiet, boy!</font>

251
00:16:41,168 --> 00:16:43,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm telling you...</font>

252
00:16:43,228 --> 00:16:45,368
<font color=#FFFF00>that I am trying my best to understand you.</font>

253
00:16:54,698 --> 00:16:56,568
<font color=#FFFF00>My children...</font>

254
00:16:56,568 --> 00:16:59,128
<font color=#FFFF00>still can't understand you. They can't forgive you yet either.</font>

255
00:17:01,128 --> 00:17:02,168
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

256
00:17:03,768 --> 00:17:05,898
<font color=#FFFF00>I sometimes...</font>

257
00:17:06,668 --> 00:17:08,468
<font color=#FFFF00>can understand you.</font>

258
00:17:09,298 --> 00:17:11,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I forgive you for a while too.</font>

259
00:17:12,168 --> 00:17:13,368
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

260
00:17:13,768 --> 00:17:17,668
<font color=#FFFF00>you were too mean to us.</font>

261
00:17:19,068 --> 00:17:21,468
<font color=#FFFF00>My son...</font>

262
00:17:21,898 --> 00:17:24,228
<font color=#FFFF00>raised Seong Joon with so much love.</font>

263
00:17:24,368 --> 00:17:26,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Regardless of what happened,</font>

264
00:17:26,668 --> 00:17:29,668
<font color=#FFFF00>I think you should thank him.</font>

265
00:17:30,498 --> 00:17:33,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Forget about everything that happened,</font>

266
00:17:34,098 --> 00:17:36,568
<font color=#FFFF00>and just think about how well Seong Joon turned out.</font>

267
00:17:36,898 --> 00:17:39,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Among the three brothers, he's the most successful one.</font>

268
00:17:39,498 --> 00:17:42,228
<font color=#FFFF00>He's also the most handsome and the most mature one.</font>

269
00:17:42,868 --> 00:17:45,068
<font color=#FFFF00>You should stop your vengeance now.</font>

270
00:17:45,168 --> 00:17:47,398
<font color=#FFFF00>When I was packing these condiments,</font>

271
00:17:48,098 --> 00:17:49,698
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought about that.</font>

272
00:17:49,928 --> 00:17:51,998
<font color=#FFFF00>And it made me feel so sad.</font>

273
00:17:53,298 --> 00:17:56,838
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know if you will care about what I say,</font>

274
00:17:57,398 --> 00:17:59,128
<font color=#FFFF00>but I've come here to tell you this...</font>

275
00:17:59,728 --> 00:18:01,128
<font color=#FFFF00>as a grandmother.</font>

276
00:18:02,168 --> 00:18:03,468
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll get going then.</font>

277
00:18:06,798 --> 00:18:08,298
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't get to move...</font>

278
00:18:08,868 --> 00:18:10,698
<font color=#FFFF00>the pots in the rooftop yet.</font>

279
00:18:11,928 --> 00:18:15,668
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know if Jeong Eun told you this.</font>

280
00:18:16,668 --> 00:18:19,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me leave them there until you tear down the house.</font>

281
00:18:20,498 --> 00:18:22,768
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a shame to waste them.</font>

282
00:18:23,628 --> 00:18:24,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Please do me a favor.</font>

283
00:18:25,498 --> 00:18:27,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm really leaving now.</font>

284
00:18:29,128 --> 00:18:30,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma'am.</font>

285
00:18:30,198 --> 00:18:31,428
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't need to come out.</font>

286
00:18:52,098 --> 00:18:53,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom,</font>

287
00:18:53,428 --> 00:18:56,668
<font color=#FFFF00>now that we're eating ramyeon together in this small house,</font>

288
00:18:56,668 --> 00:18:58,868
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like we've become Heung Bu's family.</font>

289
00:18:58,968 --> 00:19:00,798
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like we're really poor.</font>

290
00:19:02,198 --> 00:19:04,728
<font color=#FFFF00>But it's really cozy, so I don't hate it too much.</font>

291
00:19:06,898 --> 00:19:08,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say cozy?</font>

292
00:19:08,928 --> 00:19:09,968
<font color=#FFFF00>You're unbelievable.</font>

293
00:19:10,228 --> 00:19:12,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, it splattered on my clothes.</font>

294
00:19:13,198 --> 00:19:15,798
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm over 60 years old, and I'm eating ramyeon...</font>

295
00:19:15,798 --> 00:19:17,498
<font color=#FFFF00>in this small house with my grown up children.</font>

296
00:19:17,498 --> 00:19:18,868
<font color=#FFFF00>How do you call this cozy?</font>

297
00:19:18,868 --> 00:19:19,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

298
00:19:20,068 --> 00:19:22,398
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just saying that's how it feels.</font>

299
00:19:22,398 --> 00:19:25,628
<font color=#FFFF00>It would feel even better if it rains outside.</font>

300
00:19:26,068 --> 00:19:28,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, since this already happened,</font>

301
00:19:28,598 --> 00:19:31,428
<font color=#FFFF00>we should live with a positive mind.</font>

302
00:19:31,428 --> 00:19:33,398
<font color=#FFFF00>You can be positive all you want.</font>

303
00:19:33,398 --> 00:19:35,968
<font color=#FFFF00>I can never be positive.</font>

304
00:19:36,398 --> 00:19:38,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness, it smells like ramyeon.</font>

305
00:19:38,998 --> 00:19:40,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Where have you been, Mother?</font>

306
00:19:40,668 --> 00:19:41,698
<font color=#FFFF00>I went to the roof top.</font>

307
00:19:43,628 --> 00:19:44,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you go there?</font>

308
00:19:45,198 --> 00:19:47,168
<font color=#FFFF00>I got some doenjang and gochujang.</font>

309
00:19:47,428 --> 00:19:49,268
<font color=#FFFF00>And I fed Moong Chi since I already went there.</font>

310
00:19:49,268 --> 00:19:50,798
<font color=#FFFF00>You should've asked the kids to do it.</font>

311
00:19:50,798 --> 00:19:53,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would you go there and drain your energy?</font>

312
00:19:53,298 --> 00:19:56,098
<font color=#FFFF00>The real estate agent said they might tear it down soon.</font>

313
00:19:56,898 --> 00:19:59,268
<font color=#FFFF00>We need to find...</font>

314
00:19:59,728 --> 00:20:02,338
<font color=#FFFF00>a place to move her.</font>

315
00:20:02,398 --> 00:20:03,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother,</font>

316
00:20:03,498 --> 00:20:05,728
<font color=#FFFF00>eat some ramyeon.</font>

317
00:20:08,298 --> 00:20:09,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Here you go.</font>

318
00:20:10,298 --> 00:20:11,528
<font color=#FFFF00>We should be really thankful...</font>

319
00:20:11,868 --> 00:20:13,728
<font color=#FFFF00>that we can eat this ramyeon.</font>

320
00:20:17,468 --> 00:20:18,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Only if...</font>

321
00:20:18,998 --> 00:20:20,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon was smarter.</font>

322
00:20:21,528 --> 00:20:22,728
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you talking about?</font>

323
00:20:22,728 --> 00:20:24,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Think about it, Mom.</font>

324
00:20:24,468 --> 00:20:25,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon's brother,</font>

325
00:20:25,798 --> 00:20:28,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee is very rich, you know?</font>

326
00:20:29,128 --> 00:20:30,868
<font color=#FFFF00>If Seong Joon played smart,</font>

327
00:20:30,868 --> 00:20:32,498
<font color=#FFFF00>we wouldn't be here doing this.</font>

328
00:20:32,628 --> 00:20:35,798
<font color=#FFFF00>He's so tactless and loyal.</font>

329
00:20:35,898 --> 00:20:38,228
<font color=#FFFF00>He could go straight to his brother, make up with him,</font>

330
00:20:38,228 --> 00:20:41,268
<font color=#FFFF00>and talk him into giving us our house back.</font>

331
00:20:42,628 --> 00:20:43,728
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

332
00:20:44,028 --> 00:20:46,968
<font color=#FFFF00>He could even get us a nicer house. How nice would that be?</font>

333
00:20:46,968 --> 00:20:49,668
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hey! - Goodness.</font>

334
00:20:49,668 --> 00:20:51,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you not to mention Mr. Lee in front of me, didn't I?</font>

335
00:20:51,628 --> 00:20:54,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, it's just that I'm really sorry.</font>

336
00:20:54,998 --> 00:20:56,168
<font color=#FFFF00>You idiot.</font>

337
00:20:56,528 --> 00:20:58,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Is the one thing you managed to think about..</font>

338
00:20:58,928 --> 00:21:01,068
<font color=#FFFF00>is exploiting his rich brother?</font>

339
00:21:01,068 --> 00:21:02,838
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not planning to exploit him.</font>

340
00:21:03,028 --> 00:21:06,068
<font color=#FFFF00>That's a way of paying us back for everything we've done for him.</font>

341
00:21:06,628 --> 00:21:08,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom!</font>

342
00:21:08,928 --> 00:21:09,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Be quiet.</font>

343
00:21:09,928 --> 00:21:11,428
<font color=#FFFF00>What did I do?</font>

344
00:21:11,798 --> 00:21:13,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you have self-respect?</font>

345
00:21:13,728 --> 00:21:16,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't take it even if that guy will give us our house back.</font>

346
00:21:16,368 --> 00:21:18,628
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll spit on his face right away.</font>

347
00:21:18,628 --> 00:21:21,198
<font color=#FFFF00>You've gone too far.</font>

348
00:21:21,768 --> 00:21:22,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

349
00:21:22,968 --> 00:21:26,428
<font color=#FFFF00>If you think about it, Mr. Lee is a poor thing too.</font>

350
00:21:26,568 --> 00:21:27,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

351
00:21:27,768 --> 00:21:30,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Because of Hyung Seop's mistake, an innocent man died.</font>

352
00:21:30,168 --> 00:21:32,368
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why Mr. Lee and Seong Joon...</font>

353
00:21:32,368 --> 00:21:34,028
<font color=#FFFF00>became orphans overnight.</font>

354
00:21:34,338 --> 00:21:35,898
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not all that happened.</font>

355
00:21:35,968 --> 00:21:38,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee had to be parted with his only family...</font>

356
00:21:38,568 --> 00:21:41,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon for 23 long years.</font>

357
00:21:42,598 --> 00:21:46,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. Think about you becoming orphans overnight.</font>

358
00:21:47,568 --> 00:21:49,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, are you...</font>

359
00:21:49,398 --> 00:21:51,568
<font color=#FFFF00>taking sides with Mr. Lee?</font>

360
00:21:51,568 --> 00:21:53,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not taking any sides.</font>

361
00:21:53,198 --> 00:21:56,328
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just saying this because he's nothing like our children.</font>

362
00:21:56,328 --> 00:21:58,528
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean he's nothing like us?</font>

363
00:21:58,528 --> 00:22:00,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Look at our children.</font>

364
00:22:00,328 --> 00:22:02,898
<font color=#FFFF00>None of you wished to...</font>

365
00:22:02,898 --> 00:22:05,598
<font color=#FFFF00>leave your parents, and you all crawled back into the house...</font>

366
00:22:05,598 --> 00:22:06,768
<font color=#FFFF00>and created this mess.</font>

367
00:22:06,798 --> 00:22:10,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee made his own fortune and came here...</font>

368
00:22:10,498 --> 00:22:14,328
<font color=#FFFF00>with determination to find his brother.</font>

369
00:22:14,368 --> 00:22:16,528
<font color=#FFFF00>It shows how hard he's been living his life.</font>

370
00:22:16,668 --> 00:22:18,498
<font color=#FFFF00>There's nobody like him these days.</font>

371
00:22:19,728 --> 00:22:21,098
<font color=#FFFF00>So what are you saying, Grandmother?</font>

372
00:22:21,128 --> 00:22:23,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying that guy's actions are justified?</font>

373
00:22:23,468 --> 00:22:25,728
<font color=#FFFF00>That's wrong, Grandmother.</font>

374
00:22:25,928 --> 00:22:29,028
<font color=#FFFF00>He shouldn't be doing this to us. We are innocent.</font>

375
00:22:29,268 --> 00:22:31,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just saying.</font>

376
00:22:31,198 --> 00:22:33,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Just keep eating ramyeon. The noodles will get soft.</font>

377
00:22:33,928 --> 00:22:34,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

378
00:22:37,398 --> 00:22:38,598
<font color=#FFFF00>I...</font>

379
00:22:39,268 --> 00:22:42,028
<font color=#FFFF00>had to agree to play along.</font>

380
00:22:42,068 --> 00:22:44,428
<font color=#FFFF00>I felt sorry to Chang Soo and you guys.</font>

381
00:22:44,428 --> 00:22:45,968
<font color=#FFFF00>And I knew the family was going to become a mess.</font>

382
00:22:45,998 --> 00:22:48,228
<font color=#FFFF00>But I had to save the boy first.</font>

383
00:22:48,228 --> 00:22:50,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness, it's shocking.</font>

384
00:22:50,368 --> 00:22:53,668
<font color=#FFFF00>How can the eighth grader think of jumping off a building?</font>

385
00:22:55,128 --> 00:22:57,968
<font color=#FFFF00>So I think from Dr. Kang's perspective,</font>

386
00:22:58,398 --> 00:23:01,668
<font color=#FFFF00>he must have considered this to be quite a serious problem.</font>

387
00:23:02,168 --> 00:23:03,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Dr. Kang...</font>

388
00:23:03,798 --> 00:23:05,768
<font color=#FFFF00>knows how Hee Sook is.</font>

389
00:23:05,768 --> 00:23:08,398
<font color=#FFFF00>He was well aware of Ji Hoon's condition.</font>

390
00:23:08,498 --> 00:23:10,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Think about how serious it must have been for him...</font>

391
00:23:10,498 --> 00:23:12,368
<font color=#FFFF00>to use this sort of plan to save Ji Hoon.</font>

392
00:23:13,798 --> 00:23:16,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, Dr. Kang's...</font>

393
00:23:16,498 --> 00:23:17,828
<font color=#FFFF00>youngest daughter...</font>

394
00:23:18,898 --> 00:23:21,728
<font color=#FFFF00>went through something similar to what Ji Hoon went through.</font>

395
00:23:22,198 --> 00:23:25,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard she is paralyzed from the waist down.</font>

396
00:23:27,498 --> 00:23:28,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

397
00:23:29,568 --> 00:23:30,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

398
00:23:30,898 --> 00:23:32,068
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why...</font>

399
00:23:32,068 --> 00:23:33,998
<font color=#FFFF00>he overreached...</font>

400
00:23:33,998 --> 00:23:36,368
<font color=#FFFF00>so that the same thing doesn't happen to Ji Hoon.</font>

401
00:23:36,398 --> 00:23:38,068
<font color=#FFFF00>He discussed that with me.</font>

402
00:23:39,498 --> 00:23:41,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. Kids have to go through a lot these days.</font>

403
00:23:42,668 --> 00:23:44,228
<font color=#FFFF00>If this continues, a disaster is bound to strike.</font>

404
00:23:44,228 --> 00:23:46,298
<font color=#FFFF00>We ought to get rid of that college entrance exam.</font>

405
00:23:48,268 --> 00:23:49,368
<font color=#FFFF00>But still. Father,</font>

406
00:23:50,068 --> 00:23:53,298
<font color=#FFFF00>we know the truth now.</font>

407
00:23:54,398 --> 00:23:57,928
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not something we can cover up by ourselves.</font>

408
00:23:58,198 --> 00:24:00,268
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not an absolute solution.</font>

409
00:24:01,198 --> 00:24:04,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, this is between Ji Hoon and Hee Sook.</font>

410
00:24:05,168 --> 00:24:07,198
<font color=#FFFF00>We should tell Hee Sook the truth.</font>

411
00:24:07,498 --> 00:24:10,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Let them find their own solution. Don't you think this is better?</font>

412
00:24:10,998 --> 00:24:12,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

413
00:24:12,328 --> 00:24:14,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure. Hee Sook will be thrilled to find the solution.</font>

414
00:24:15,168 --> 00:24:16,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you know that with Chang Soo's success,</font>

415
00:24:16,498 --> 00:24:18,768
<font color=#FFFF00>she is more confident about her education method than ever?</font>

416
00:24:19,968 --> 00:24:21,568
