<font color=#FFFF00>(Hearty Sanatorium)</font>

833
00:49:34,228 --> 00:49:35,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

834
00:49:35,998 --> 00:49:38,528
<font color=#FFFF00>The old sayings are true.</font>

835
00:49:38,798 --> 00:49:39,798
<font color=#FFFF00>There are no parents in this world...</font>

836
00:49:40,328 --> 00:49:42,998
<font color=#FFFF00>who wouldn't do anything for their child.</font>

837
00:49:44,128 --> 00:49:46,028
<font color=#FFFF00>It was going to turn out like this anyway.</font>

838
00:49:46,398 --> 00:49:48,268
<font color=#FFFF00>So if you fixed it earlier,</font>

839
00:49:48,868 --> 00:49:51,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Jeong didn't have to struggle.</font>

840
00:49:51,568 --> 00:49:54,528
<font color=#FFFF00>She could've lived a happy life.</font>

841
00:49:58,128 --> 00:50:00,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Now, it's about time.</font>

842
00:50:01,128 --> 00:50:03,528
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the will the bank has been keeping for you.</font>

843
00:50:05,128 --> 00:50:07,628
<font color=#FFFF00>And this is Hyun Jeong's stock certificate.</font>

844
00:50:07,968 --> 00:50:09,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Gui Boon gave up as well.</font>

845
00:50:10,468 --> 00:50:11,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Now, you just have...</font>

846
00:50:13,568 --> 00:50:15,928
<font color=#FFFF00>to fix your will.</font>

847
00:50:16,498 --> 00:50:18,098
<font color=#FFFF00>In my whole life,</font>

848
00:50:19,268 --> 00:50:22,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I began as a street vendor...</font>

849
00:50:22,028 --> 00:50:24,368
<font color=#FFFF00>and managed to save that much money.</font>

850
00:50:26,368 --> 00:50:29,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I just wanted to feed, dress,</font>

851
00:50:29,898 --> 00:50:32,828
<font color=#FFFF00>and educate my children well.</font>

852
00:50:33,328 --> 00:50:36,528
<font color=#FFFF00>But that money became my enemy.</font>

853
00:50:37,668 --> 00:50:39,668
<font color=#FFFF00>That money pulled siblings apart,</font>

854
00:50:39,928 --> 00:50:40,968
<font color=#FFFF00>and that money...</font>

855
00:50:41,398 --> 00:50:44,128
<font color=#FFFF00>also pulled apart the parent from her children.</font>

856
00:50:55,068 --> 00:50:57,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Come closer.</font>

857
00:51:00,898 --> 00:51:01,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

858
00:51:04,128 --> 00:51:05,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

859
00:51:05,898 --> 00:51:07,768
<font color=#FFFF00>You grew up as a beautiful lady.</font>

860
00:51:09,928 --> 00:51:12,298
<font color=#FFFF00>You became a beautiful lady.</font>

861
00:51:13,798 --> 00:51:15,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

862
00:51:16,498 --> 00:51:18,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't say that.</font>

863
00:51:19,128 --> 00:51:21,768
<font color=#FFFF00>There's nothing you should be sorry about.</font>

864
00:51:23,268 --> 00:51:24,768
<font color=#FFFF00>I am the one...</font>

865
00:51:25,898 --> 00:51:28,098
<font color=#FFFF00>who is sorry.</font>

866
00:51:29,898 --> 00:51:31,898
<font color=#FFFF00>- Grandmother. - Yes?</font>

867
00:51:33,328 --> 00:51:34,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Just...</font>

868
00:51:35,098 --> 00:51:37,868
<font color=#FFFF00>fix the will for him.</font>

869
00:51:39,768 --> 00:51:40,828
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

870
00:51:42,228 --> 00:51:43,928
<font color=#FFFF00>But you...</font>

871
00:51:46,168 --> 00:51:49,098
<font color=#FFFF00>won't be taking anything then.</font>

872
00:51:50,068 --> 00:51:52,198
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't need anything.</font>

873
00:51:53,028 --> 00:51:55,368
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been living that way until now.</font>

874
00:51:56,328 --> 00:51:57,598
<font color=#FFFF00>So Grandmother,</font>

875
00:51:57,868 --> 00:51:59,728
<font color=#FFFF00>don't worry about me...</font>

876
00:52:00,328 --> 00:52:01,628
<font color=#FFFF00>and just...</font>

877
00:52:02,098 --> 00:52:03,668
<font color=#FFFF00>fix the will.</font>

878
00:52:05,398 --> 00:52:06,768
<font color=#FFFF00>You've been stuck here...</font>

879
00:52:07,028 --> 00:52:08,868
<font color=#FFFF00>for the past 20 years.</font>

880
00:52:09,568 --> 00:52:12,328
<font color=#FFFF00>You spent too many years in here.</font>

881
00:52:12,698 --> 00:52:14,028
<font color=#FFFF00>My darling.</font>

882
00:52:15,328 --> 00:52:16,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Come closer.</font>

883
00:52:18,328 --> 00:52:20,228
<font color=#FFFF00>My darling.</font>

884
00:52:20,698 --> 00:52:22,568
<font color=#FFFF00>My lovely darling.</font>

885
00:52:22,568 --> 00:52:24,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me hug you.</font>

886
00:52:25,068 --> 00:52:26,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

887
00:52:28,068 --> 00:52:29,328
<font color=#FFFF00>My darling.</font>

888
00:52:29,968 --> 00:52:31,598
<font color=#FFFF00>My lovely darling.</font>

889
00:52:32,168 --> 00:52:33,368
<font color=#FFFF00>My darling.</font>

890
00:52:34,728 --> 00:52:38,168
<font color=#FFFF00>(Testament)</font>

891
00:52:46,528 --> 00:52:47,528
<font color=#FFFF00>(Park Chang Wook)</font>

892
00:52:47,868 --> 00:52:48,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay!</font>

893
00:52:50,898 --> 00:52:53,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I waited for 20 years. 20 years, I tell you.</font>

894
00:52:55,028 --> 00:52:57,468
<font color=#FFFF00>It has turned my hair gray.</font>

895
00:52:59,628 --> 00:53:00,668
<font color=#FFFF00>I have one condition.</font>

896
00:53:01,628 --> 00:53:03,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I want you...</font>

897
00:53:04,028 --> 00:53:05,698
<font color=#FFFF00>to release...</font>

898
00:53:06,398 --> 00:53:07,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui and Gui Boon.</font>

899
00:53:09,068 --> 00:53:10,928
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mr. Kim. - Yes, sir.</font>

900
00:53:11,598 --> 00:53:13,298
<font color=#FFFF00>- Take care of this. - Yes, sir.</font>

901
00:53:16,968 --> 00:53:20,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I was going to release them anyway.</font>

902
00:53:21,028 --> 00:53:23,628
<font color=#FFFF00>They don't have a penny to their names.</font>

903
00:53:24,398 --> 00:53:25,698
<font color=#FFFF00>She will live...</font>

904
00:53:26,168 --> 00:53:28,728
<font color=#FFFF00>as Oh Dong Hui for the rest of her life.</font>

905
00:53:28,728 --> 00:53:29,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think so?</font>

906
00:53:33,998 --> 00:53:38,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, my dear Ye Bin. You're studying English.</font>

907
00:53:38,528 --> 00:53:41,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. I don't want to study English.</font>

908
00:53:41,468 --> 00:53:46,028
<font color=#FFFF00>You have to. You know Chang Soo came first place in his competition.</font>

909
00:53:46,368 --> 00:53:50,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Children are supposed to study.</font>

910
00:53:51,068 --> 00:53:53,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I want to go out and play.</font>

911
00:53:53,698 --> 00:53:54,828
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't!</font>

912
00:53:55,628 --> 00:53:57,368
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ji Hoon, stop right there. - No.</font>

913
00:53:57,498 --> 00:53:59,068
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to stop.</font>

914
00:53:59,128 --> 00:54:00,868
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing, Hee Sook?</font>

915
00:54:01,068 --> 00:54:02,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to me?</font>

916
00:54:04,498 --> 00:54:05,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Is this your report card?</font>

917
00:54:06,128 --> 00:54:08,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are your grades so terrible?</font>

918
00:54:10,328 --> 00:54:11,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you closing your ears?</font>

919
00:54:11,998 --> 00:54:13,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop closing your ears!</font>

920
00:54:15,868 --> 00:54:17,228
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

921
00:54:17,228 --> 00:54:19,728
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's the matter? - Hee Sook.</font>

922
00:54:19,828 --> 00:54:21,668
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

923
00:54:21,668 --> 00:54:22,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

924
00:54:24,128 --> 00:54:26,498
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nothing.</font>

925
00:54:26,568 --> 00:54:28,268
<font color=#FFFF00>It's no big deal.</font>

926
00:54:28,628 --> 00:54:31,398
<font color=#FFFF00>I was talking to Ji Hoon.</font>

927
00:54:31,928 --> 00:54:33,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Ji Hoon, follow me.</font>

928
00:54:33,698 --> 00:54:34,728
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

929
00:54:34,798 --> 00:54:36,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not talking to you.</font>

930
00:54:38,668 --> 00:54:40,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Please excuse him.</font>

931
00:54:40,628 --> 00:54:44,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon must have been stressed out with studying.</font>

932
00:54:44,798 --> 00:54:45,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Follow me.</font>

933
00:54:46,228 --> 00:54:48,098
<font color=#FFFF00>- I said no! - Gosh.</font>

934
00:54:48,128 --> 00:54:49,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey!</font>

935
00:54:49,728 --> 00:54:53,198
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you think you are doing to your Mom?</font>

936
00:54:54,198 --> 00:54:55,228
<font color=#FFFF00>I mean,</font>

937
00:54:55,498 --> 00:54:57,868
<font color=#FFFF00>she's your aunt.</font>

938
00:55:02,228 --> 00:55:05,298
<font color=#FFFF00>He must be under a lot of stress.</font>

939
00:55:06,298 --> 00:55:09,598
<font color=#FFFF00>You should stop it. Ji Hoon is not your son.</font>

940
00:55:09,598 --> 00:55:11,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to Hye Joo's son?</font>

941
00:55:11,668 --> 00:55:13,728
<font color=#FFFF00>I just can't understand you.</font>

942
00:55:13,728 --> 00:55:15,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother. You know that.</font>

943
00:55:16,028 --> 00:55:17,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon and Hye Joo are...</font>

944
00:55:17,768 --> 00:55:20,398
<font color=#FFFF00>not that interested in their child's education.</font>

945
00:55:20,628 --> 00:55:23,228
<font color=#FFFF00>If Ji Hoon studies a little harder,</font>

946
00:55:23,298 --> 00:55:25,368
<font color=#FFFF00>he will get first place in his school again.</font>

947
00:55:25,698 --> 00:55:27,628
<font color=#FFFF00>He will even take the nation's first place.</font>

948
00:55:28,098 --> 00:55:30,198
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ji Hoon, follow me. - No.</font>

949
00:55:30,198 --> 00:55:32,668
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook, stop it.</font>

950
00:55:32,668 --> 00:55:35,428
<font color=#FFFF00>You can lead a horse to the water, but you can't make him drink.</font>

951
00:55:35,498 --> 00:55:38,668
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no way you can force him to study when he doesn't want to.</font>

952
00:55:39,298 --> 00:55:41,268
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe this. Honey.</font>

953
00:55:41,598 --> 00:55:43,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's just focus on Chang Soo.</font>

954
00:55:43,998 --> 00:55:46,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon is not our son anymore. Why are you doing this?</font>

955
00:55:46,768 --> 00:55:49,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Just give him to Seong Hoon and forget about him.</font>

956
00:55:51,498 --> 00:55:52,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother, Mother, and Father.</font>

957
00:55:53,128 --> 00:55:54,468
<font color=#FFFF00>And members of this family.</font>

958
00:55:55,928 --> 00:55:57,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I raised him for 15 years.</font>

959
00:55:58,198 --> 00:55:59,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Even though...</font>

960
00:55:59,698 --> 00:56:01,428
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't give birth to him,</font>

961
00:56:02,168 --> 00:56:05,568
<font color=#FFFF00>I raised him with all my heart for 15 years.</font>

962
00:56:05,728 --> 00:56:08,928
<font color=#FFFF00>We are living under the same roof after all.</font>

963
00:56:09,098 --> 00:56:12,528
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't matter whether he's my birth son or not.</font>

964
00:56:13,328 --> 00:56:16,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's just make the most of our special abilities. You make money.</font>

965
00:56:16,728 --> 00:56:19,798
<font color=#FFFF00>And I will be in charge of children's education.</font>

966
00:56:19,828 --> 00:56:22,798
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with that?</font>

967
00:56:22,798 --> 00:56:26,168
<font color=#FFFF00>The problem is Ji Hoon doesn't want it.</font>

968
00:56:26,498 --> 00:56:29,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo, take Ji Hoon with you.</font>

969
00:56:29,968 --> 00:56:31,998
<font color=#FFFF00>- Okay. - Bring him.</font>

970
00:56:32,198 --> 00:56:34,498
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't go. Follow me.</font>

971
00:56:34,498 --> 00:56:37,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook, let go of him.</font>

972
00:56:37,268 --> 00:56:39,368
<font color=#FFFF00>You should let go of him.</font>

973
00:56:39,468 --> 00:56:41,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon needs to study.</font>

974
00:56:42,428 --> 00:56:45,168
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you think you are doing with him?</font>

975
00:56:46,828 --> 00:56:47,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook.</font>

976
00:56:48,168 --> 00:56:49,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Follow me!</font>

977
00:56:49,868 --> 00:56:51,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Kang Hee Sook!</font>

978
00:56:51,568 --> 00:56:52,998
<font color=#FFFF00>You wicked wench!</font>

979
00:56:53,298 --> 00:56:55,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you want to see him die?</font>

980
00:56:55,298 --> 00:56:56,928
<font color=#FFFF00>I said he needs to study.</font>

981
00:56:56,968 --> 00:56:59,628
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hee Sook, stop it. - Hee Sook.</font>

982
00:56:59,628 --> 00:57:01,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you out of your mind?</font>

983
00:57:02,498 --> 00:57:04,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it, everyone!</font>

984
00:57:04,928 --> 00:57:08,098
<font color=#FFFF00>If you keep doing this, I'll run away from home.</font>

985
00:57:09,028 --> 00:57:12,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon. Ji Hoon!</font>

986
00:57:12,628 --> 00:57:15,228
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ji Hoon, you rascal! - Hee Sook!</font>

987
00:57:16,228 --> 00:57:17,968
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to stop!</font>

988
00:57:23,228 --> 00:57:24,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you see that?</font>

989
00:57:26,528 --> 00:57:27,598
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes. - Yes.</font>

990
00:57:27,798 --> 00:57:29,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I did.</font>

991
00:57:29,628 --> 00:57:31,098
<font color=#FFFF00>It's that bad.</font>

992
00:57:31,728 --> 00:57:33,398
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think...</font>

993
00:57:33,568 --> 00:57:36,698
<font color=#FFFF00>it is a good idea to tell her the truth now.</font>

994
00:57:37,028 --> 00:57:40,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I know. That's exactly what I'm saying.</font>

995
00:57:43,298 --> 00:57:44,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

996
00:57:46,968 --> 00:57:48,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Still.</font>

997
00:57:49,228 --> 00:57:53,128
<font color=#FFFF00>How long do we have to do this?</font>

998
00:57:54,168 --> 00:57:56,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's say we will let it slide this time.</font>

999
00:57:56,798 --> 00:57:58,698
<font color=#FFFF00>But after quite a while,</font>

1000
00:57:58,968 --> 00:58:00,928
<font color=#FFFF00>how will you tell them the truth?</font>

1001
00:58:01,628 --> 00:58:03,568
<font color=#FFFF00>You're right.</font>

1002
00:58:03,798 --> 00:58:06,328
<font color=#FFFF00>This is driving me crazy. What should we do?</font>

1003
00:58:12,428 --> 00:58:13,898
<font color=#FFFF00>It wasn't me.</font>

1004
00:58:17,368 --> 00:58:18,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Was it you, Dad?</font>

1005
00:58:20,898 --> 00:58:21,928
<font color=#FFFF00>It wasn't me.</font>

1006
00:58:23,968 --> 00:58:25,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Who would it be then?</font>

1007
00:58:31,828 --> 00:58:32,898
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that true?</font>

1008
00:58:34,968 --> 00:58:38,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, since when were you there?</font>

1009
00:58:38,728 --> 00:58:39,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

1010
00:58:40,298 --> 00:58:42,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo, what did you hear?</font>

1011
00:58:43,268 --> 00:58:44,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that true?</font>

1012
00:58:44,998 --> 00:58:46,698
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - What?</font>

1013
00:58:48,098 --> 00:58:51,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true that Ji Hoon and I weren't switched?</font>

1014
00:58:54,668 --> 00:58:56,528
<font color=#FFFF00>What should we do?</font>

1015
00:58:57,198 --> 00:58:59,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Was it really a lie?</font>

1016
00:59:00,368 --> 00:59:01,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that it?</font>

1017
00:59:02,168 --> 00:59:04,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad. Mom.</font>

1018
00:59:04,498 --> 00:59:05,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandfather.</font>

1019
00:59:05,698 --> 00:59:07,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Keep quiet.</font>

1020
00:59:07,268 --> 00:59:08,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to him?</font>

1021
00:59:08,998 --> 00:59:10,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Stay quiet.</font>

1022
00:59:10,928 --> 00:59:12,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it really true?</font>

1023
00:59:12,468 --> 00:59:14,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true that we were not switched?</font>

1024
00:59:14,928 --> 00:59:16,498
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to be quiet.</font>

1025
00:59:16,498 --> 00:59:18,728
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon, stop covering his mouth with your hand.</font>

1026
00:59:18,728 --> 00:59:20,868
<font color=#FFFF00>- Keep quiet. - Stop it.</font>

1027
00:59:28,328 --> 00:59:30,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother, are you okay?</font>

1028
00:59:30,868 --> 00:59:33,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I'm fine.</font>

1029
00:59:34,228 --> 00:59:38,098
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, go give Seong Joon a call.</font>

1030
00:59:38,328 --> 00:59:41,098
<font color=#FFFF00>He's taking care of everything all alone.</font>

1031
00:59:42,098 --> 00:59:44,398
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm afraid if he'd be in danger.</font>

1032
00:59:44,698 --> 00:59:47,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Go give him a call now.</font>

1033
00:59:50,468 --> 00:59:51,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

1034
00:59:59,028 --> 01:00:00,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon, it's me.</font>

1035
01:00:02,628 --> 01:00:03,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, we are out.</font>

1036
01:00:04,468 --> 01:00:06,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother and I got out of the house.</font>

1037
01:00:17,198 --> 01:00:18,368
<font color=#FFFF00>Moong Chi.</font>

1038
01:00:20,998 --> 01:00:22,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Moong Chi.</font>

1039
01:00:22,998 --> 01:00:25,268
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing here alone?</font>

